hotel_data.name: Club Wyndham Canterbury
hotel_data.hotel_description: Located within 2.5 miles of Fishermanâ€™s Wharf and Ghirardelli Square, this hotel offers spacious suites with fully equipped kitchenettes and free WiFi. A gym and business centre are also located on site. A living room with a sofa bed and a cable TV is furnished in all suites at Club Wyndham Canterbury. The modern rooms feature bright color accents and include a large bathroom with bath amenities. The San Francisco Wyndham Canterbury offers a game room with billiards for guest use. Meeting rooms are also available on site. Alcatraz Cruises and the Aquarium of the Bay are each less than 3 miles from this hotel. Golden Gate Bridge is about 4 miles away.

hotel_data.name: St. Regis San Francisco
hotel_data.hotel_description: Featuring a full service spa, an indoor infinity pool and an on-site restaurant, this luxury hotel is located in the SOMA District of San Francisco. A flat-screen TV is included in each guest room. Union Square is 8 minutesâ€™ walk away. A luxurious bathroom with a soaking tub and a TV is featured in all guest rooms at St. Regis San Francisco. Each elegantly decorated room boasts a minibar and a DVD player. Guests of St. Regis San Francisco can enjoy breakfast, lunch and dinner at the Grill restaurant. The restaurant features grilled meats, fish, burgers and an oyster bar in an intimate setting. Signature cocktails and a bar menu are offered at St. Regis Lobby Lounge. Located on-site, Remede Spa provides separate whirlpools, steam rooms and saunas for men and women. Guests can enjoy chilled champagne and handmade truffles before seeing a spa therapist. Information regarding area events and activities can be requested at the concierge desk. The St. Regis San Francisco is across the street from Yerba Buena Gardens. AT&T Park is 1.6 km away.
